    "longBusinessSummary": "Rang Dong Light Source & Vacuum Flask Joint Stock Company manufactures and sells general lighting products in Vietnam. It operates through Light Bulbs, Thermos Flasks, and Other Products segments. The company offers lamps and tubes; indoor luminaires, including LED panels, battens, ceiling products, cross and linear lights, parking and high bay lights, downlights, and track lights, as well as LED home lighting products; and outdoor luminaires, such as LED flood and streetlights. It also provides professional lighting solutions comprising LED grow light high bay lights, LED fishing lights, underwater lights, LED light for dragon fruit growing, and grow lights; human centric lighting products; smart home, city, and farm products; light bulbs, lighting tools, glass products, and thermoses; and renewable energy lighting products, vacuum flasks, and household appliances. In addition, the company engages in professional ODM/OEM services for lighting products; scientific and technical services; technology transfer; direct import and export; and consulting and lighting design, as well as lighting equipment repair and installation services for the civil and industrial sectors. Rang Dong Light Source & Vacuum Flask Joint Stock Company was founded in 1958 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
